data.description: REDUCED PRICE  LOCATION LOCATION!   Phase 3 move in ready home.  Curb appeal plus gorgeous landscaped backyard featuring synthetic turf.  The new sylish front door brings you into a spacious great room with soaring ceilings and skylight and patio view.  Kitchen features recently updated stainless  counter depth refrigerator , double oven stove and dishwasher,,  The owner's bedroom  and bath are spacious with a good size walk-in closet.  Indoor laundry with newer washer/dryer and cabinets.  This pristine home has newer floors, hardware, faucets, lighting...  AC and roof are in good condition and the rest is covered by professionally managed HOA.  ALL OFFERS CONSIDERED.  Close to Pickleball, Golf, Pools, Clay Club, Shopping, Churches etc.  You will find your new home here.  A must see!
